{"prompt": "Generate a sleek website for a legal consulting group. The brand color should be a classic charcoal grey.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Apex Legal Consulting</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            background-color: #2c3e50; /* Charcoal grey */\n            color: #ecf0f1; /* Light grey for text */\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, #34495e, #2c3e50); /* Darker grey gradient */\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 3px solid #bdc3c7; /* Lighter grey border */\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: #ecf0f1;\n        }\n        header p {\n            margin-top: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            color: #bdc3c7;\n        }\n        section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n        }\n        #hero {\n            text-align: center;\n            background: url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x500/2c3e50/ecf0f1?text=Elegant+Legal+Solutions') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            height: 60vh;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            color: #ecf0f1;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n        #hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background-color: rgba(44, 62, 80, 0.7); /* Overlay for readability */\n        }\n        #hero .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: #ecf0f1;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            color: #bdc3c7;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);\n        }\n        h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: #ecf0f1;\n        }\n        .service-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: #34495e; /* Slightly lighter grey */\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border: 1px solid #2c3e50;\n        }\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n            border-color: #bdc3c7;\n        }\n        .service-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: #bdc3c7;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .service-item h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            color: #ecf0f1;\n        }\n        .service-item p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            color: #bdc3c7;\n        }\n        #contact {\n            background-color: #34495e;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #contact .contact-info {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            color: #bdc3c7;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        .contact-form {\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            gap: 15px;\n        }\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            padding: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #2c3e50;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            background-color: #2c3e50;\n            color: #ecf0f1;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n        .contact-form input::placeholder,\n        .contact-form textarea::placeholder {\n            color: #7f8c8d; /* Darker placeholder */\n        }\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: #2c3e50; /* Charcoal grey */\n            color: #ecf0f1;\n            border: none;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid #bdc3c7;\n        }\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #bdc3c7; /* Lighter grey on hover */\n            color: #2c3e50; /* Darker text on hover */\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #2c3e50;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 0; /* Remove default margin-top */\n            border-top: 3px solid #bdc3c7;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            color: #bdc3c7;\n        }\n        /* Font Awesome for Icons */\n        @import url('https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css');\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Apex Legal Consulting</h1>\n            <p>Strategic Counsel for Your Business Success</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-content\">\n            <h2>Navigating Complexity, Delivering Clarity</h2>\n            <p>Expert legal solutions tailored to your unique challenges.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Expertise</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-balance-scale\"></i>\n                    <h3>Corporate Law</h3>\n                    <p>Comprehensive services for business formation, compliance, and governance.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-file-contract\"></i>\n                    <h3>Contract Negotiation</h3>\n                    <p>Crafting and reviewing agreements to protect your interests.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-handshake\"></i>\n                    <h3>Mergers & Acquisitions</h3>\n                    <p>Guidance through intricate transactions for seamless integration.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-gavel\"></i>\n                    <h3>Litigation Support</h3>\n                    <p>Strategic defense and proactive legal representation.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p style=\"text-align: center; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; font-size: 1.2em; color: #bdc3c7;\">\n                Apex Legal Consulting is dedicated to providing unparalleled legal advisory services. Our seasoned team of legal professionals combines deep industry knowledge with a client-centric approach to deliver effective, innovative, and pragmatic solutions. We pride ourselves on building strong, lasting relationships based on trust, integrity, and a shared commitment to achieving your objectives.\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p class=\"contact-info\">Let's discuss how we can support your legal needs.</p>\n            <form class=\"contact-form\">\n                <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Apex Legal Consulting. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple JavaScript for potential future enhancements (e.g., smooth scrolling)\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}